anl.verdi.data

Interface DataReader<T extends Dataset>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataReader

    public interface DataReader<T extends Dataset>
    Interface for classes that handle reading data from datasets. This data could be originally from a file or from a model or other source.
